com.poesys.db.dao

Class PoesysTrackingThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • com.poesys.db.dao.PoesysTrackingThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class PoesysTrackingThread
extends java.lang.Thread
    A Thread object that contains the retrieval and processing state of a Poesys/DB object tree retrieval. The class tracks the set of retrieved objects as a history of objects retrieved. Each object is in a container object that has attributes related to Poesys/DB processing. The Thread subclass thus provides a container for operations involving multiple objects and provides a place outside the objects to track processing.
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
